      "startTime": 8.9333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "呼び方はなんでもいいから、投球に集中するんだ\nワンバンでもいいから、力み過ぎて怪我しないようにな",
      "startTime": 12.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ワンワン？\nワンちゃんの真似をしながら投げるんですか？",
      "startTime": 17.7508399963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、今のは忘れてくれ。まずはやってみよう",
      "startTime": 21.2175076802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.9617713768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！　軽く投げてみます！\n……えいっ！",
      "startTime": 28.6951047102,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4033.333333399998,
          "startTime": 28.9951047102
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ball-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4904.895289899997,
          "startTime": 29.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bang-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5071.561956499998,
          "startTime": 30.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.6951047102
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.5284366448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　思ってたより速い？\nあっ、でも、コースが……",
      "startTime": 33.7999986013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9484365303
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、変な所に飛んでっちゃいました～\nう～ん、ボールのコントロールって難しいんですね",
      "startTime": 40.4817698637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "初めてなんだから仕方ないよ\nそれよりボールが速くて驚いたな。いい肩をしてるよ",
      "startTime": 48.8333306631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.4457827726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？\nでも、国体の選手さんはもっと速かったです",
      "startTime": 55.4124494392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.7124486763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "基準が高過ぎないか……？\nでも安心したよ。後はコントロールだけだな",
      "startTime": 62.466665268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。さっきは力を抜き過ぎちゃって\nボールがすっぽ抜けちゃったみたいで……",
      "startTime": 70.8581173736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.4581214426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "――だから、次は本気でいきますね",
      "startTime": 74.4581214426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.9247931955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　さっきより速いのが来るのか？\n待ってくれ、まだ準備が……",
      "startTime": 80.9333319347,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6134.356116999996,
          "startTime": 87.0676880517
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.4426462648
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5093129315
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "私の肩なら、もう温まったので大丈夫です！\nええーいっ！",
      "startTime": 86.5093129315,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4590.685669799996,
          "startTime": 91.0999986013
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ball-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4581.874585400002,
          "startTime": 91.0911875169
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bang-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4757.352336399989,
          "startTime": 91.2666652679
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こ、これは速過ぎ……ぐわっ！",
      "startTime": 88.3426462648,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3461.678075800009,
          "startTime": 91.8043243406
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3426462648
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.8043243406
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.5376576739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい！\n大丈夫ですか、コーチ！？",
      "startTime": 93.8376576739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.29999911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫……急所は外れてるから……\n今のは、ど真ん中だ。さくら、ナイスピッチ……",
      "startTime": 100.29999911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2024196622
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "コーチの顔が危険な色に……！？\nコーチ？　コーチーー！？",
      "startTime": 109.3024196622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5357529955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ふう、なんとか一命は取りとめたな……",
      "startTime": 116.6690934496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "酷い目に遭わせてしまって、本当にごめんなさい……\nこの後の練習は、私一人で大丈夫ですから",
      "startTime": 126.1453951618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.5951177595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんだ。最後まで付き合うよ",
      "startTime": 130.5951177595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……{user}さんに\nこれ以上怪我をさせちゃったら、私……",
      "startTime": 138.7679783659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.3346368946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……プロテクターを借りてくる。それなら平気だ\n練習時間はあまりないから、早く再開しよう",
      "startTime": 146.8999986013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.1982698597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですか？　ありがとうございます\n{user}さん！　いえ、コーチ！",
      "startTime": 153.6649365263,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4966.6498821000005,
          "startTime": 158.6315864084
        }
      ]
    },
    {
